verbose_text: Further investigation of the synergistic effects of Ezhu and Yanhusuo indicated that combination treatments of Ezhu and Yanhusuo at a ratio of 3:2 could reduce the proliferative and invasive capacities of breast cancer cells more significantly and induce more cytochrome c release (which initiates apoptosis) than the individual treatment with either Ezhu or Yanhusuo.
